Product details of Nose Up Nose Lifting Clip (Pink)

Get the nose shape that you've always wanted and increase your self-esteem with a Non-Surgical Professional Nose Lifter. Its a great alternative that eliminates the need for rhinoplasty. The Nose Up reshapes your nose to improve its general appearance with a commercial-grade plastic and rubber padded nasal molder. It generates 25degree Celsius temperature to efficiently reshape the nasal cartilage. It effectively molds and changes your noses cartilage with the right amount of pressure and warmth so you can see your nose correct itself in little time. Get the right nose shape by using the lifter regularly for just 1 month adaptive period for your desired results. Pair the Nose Up with the nutritional supplement available at Lazada and be at the top of your health and beauty game.
